INTEGRATE SAO DERIVED MODELS WITH NASA JSC CHAMBER MODELS AND OTHER GSE MODELS TO PROVIDE A SINGLE, HIGHLY SPECIALIZED AND UNIQUE TEST MODE. PERFORM PATHFINDER THERMAL DISTORTION ANALYSIS USING OUR INDEPENDENT DEVELOPED HIGHLY SPECIALIZED FEMS.
